"configuration, and infrastructure-related settings."
msgstr ""
"Bem-vindo ao Painel Administrativo do Grylli. Utilize os links abaixo para "
"gerenciar o sistema."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:15
msgid "Manage Users"
msgstr "Gerenciar Usuários"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:16
msgid ""
"Create, edit, enable/disable, or delete user accounts. Control MFA, roles, "
"and recovery access."
msgstr "Crie, edite, habilite/desabilite ou exclua contas de usuário."

